{"tid":256021,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屢於車廂內以下體頂女童臀 港鐵職員判囚4個月","createTime":"2017-05-24T08:31:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-24T11:23:43.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3f3b82e80b54ee18ec61942cc9910ff669131c73","tid":256021,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T08:31:06.000Z","msg":"港鐵職員分別於上月及本月的兩天，先後兩次在輕鐵車廂內以下體頂向同一名14歲女乘客的臀部，結果被控非禮罪。港鐵職員今在裁判法院承認兩罪，被判入獄4個月。<br />\n<br />\n被告蔡展豪(41歲)承認於上月27日及本月2日犯案。控方指上月27日早上，事主乘搭的輕鐵駛離大興北站車站時，她感到臀部被硬物觸碰，轉身只見被告以下體頂其臀部，事主未有作聲，直至列車駛至兩個站後的鳴琴站事主下車期間，被告仍不時以下體觸碰事主。<br />\n<br />\n至本月2日早上，事主乘搭輕鐵期間，當在列車駛離大興北站車站時，又再感到臀部被觸碰，轉身望見到同是被告，事主及後下車並報警。警方於5月8日在兆康站將被告拘捕，警誡下被告否認犯案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56736037&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170524\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56736037%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170524&d=K6Hxr2sAvescS5eMpjBEQMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=c18b064a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56736037%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170524&h=7be88e97\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56736037&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170524</a>"},{"pid":"685d0c45b83eda843ac9df5a3a491ee60c074c6c","tid":256021,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T08:54:40.000Z","msg":"同一名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係抵撚你死"},{"pid":"4aedefbd3fe9d030320b3641b020405a1deb5122","tid":256021,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T08:58:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e68bcdf9f7c6b57244603b23492ebd5f928f0d9","tid":256021,"uid":48142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-2